snippet.title: Blickel Trailer
snippet.description:
Blickel Is a action Platformer for the NES where your goal is to get to a a hidden treasure burred deep in a cave filled with monsters. Run, Jump, and Blast your way through four unique worlds and fight a legendary boss to claim the treasure for yourself.
